Great movie to watch.  Tons of action & drama.  Based on a pilot who's under some kind of control, which seeks attacks on society.

Imagine if you will, 'Top Gun', the famous fighter plane movie with Tom Cruise, but with Maverick (Tom's character) snapping from what appears to be PTSD, and shooting down his allies, while carrying a nuke, with a mission to destroy Las Vegas, because he's a 'messenger of God'.  This is a great gem of a movie, with William O' Leary delivering a great performance as a pilot that slowly loses his mind and goes on a rampage.  Lots of action, and quite a few hard-to-watch, unpredictable scenes. Recommended!
Good, thoughtful "What If" movie. Had this on VHS, and waited years for it to come out on DVD.
